  "notes": "Great-grandmother. Born in Baxley, Appling County, GA. Father: James H. Smith (1843-1913), died in Baxley, GA. Married Thadius Horry Sanderson. Four sons: Horry Lee (1901-1971), Norman P. (1904-), Albert Evans (1905-1946), John Jackson (1908-). Husband Thadius died 1913 in Georgia. Mary Elizabeth died 1917 in Georgia at age 32, leaving her sons orphaned — Albert Evans was just 12."
